column1: omubunge wa Kimilili Didmus Barasa aba mubweyangu bwewbweni khurumikhila limotole liua CDF bulayi mukaunty ye Bungoma
column2:
Omubunge wa Kimililili DidmasBarasa niye orumikhile limotole lia cdf bulayi mukhungona chiproject cha cdf mukaunty ye bungoma nende chikaunty chosi khukhwama western kenya.
kano kamakhurwa abuwanga nende kumukanda kwa bumenelesi kwa mizani africa. mu bumenelesi obwo mulirambo lilamba lisasa lia kimilili liamakhuba mubweyangu bwa 14.barasa anyolile kamakisi ako khukhwamanana nende bubwombakhi bwe bisomelo, chingila nende khuana busrasy ye babana bakhenyalila tawe.omujumbe wa kiharu ndindi nyoro niye obele we ebweni mukenya mwosi.omwimelesi we kumukanda kwa mizani africa abele nabululila mbo baba nebakendelelakamasasa kosi ke bujumbe akari we kumwiko kwa 2017-2018

column1: Seneta wa Narok Ledama ole Kina atilwa khu madai kekhuachilisia banakenya
column2: Polisi  ba Kilimani bamakhutila seneta wa Narok Ledama ole Kina enje weofisi ya sulwe fm eyimelelwa nende Royalmedia services khulondekhna nende matamushi kewe kabolekhana khubamo bufwisi bunyala bwakholelela sisyaumba  akarikari webanakenya.Seneta oyo atililwe bise bititi busa enyuma wekhukhwama mumahojiano ke ripoti ya BBI  mutv ya CitizeN .

column1: Kumulilo mulirumbi lia Nzoia khukhwamanana nende kasoro ye luwaya lwa sitima
column2: Batalamu babasomela khusima kumulilo khukhwama muserikali ye kaunty ye Bungoma mubuambani nende bakholi be lishini lia nzoia sugar bakholile kosi kanyalikhna khusima kumulilo kubele nekuambisie kimiba kibele muyard nikio abele benya khusya esukari silo sie khukhwinyukhila luno.kabolekhana mbo kumulimo okwo kwamanane nende hitilafu ye luwaya lwa stima.chairman we factory yino omwami joash wamangoli alala nende md wanjala makokha bakhupile orio bakholi abo nekhulimo abo ba serikali ye kaunty ye bungoma khuokoa kumulilo okwo.wamangoli abola mbo kakhaba kario kumulilo okwo sekurerire asara engali tawe

column1: Bapolisi be ekitali bali bureke khufunanisia kumusango basani babili balomekha khukhwira omuloosi omukeni khukhwama swizterland
column2: Bapolisi musirimba sie ekitali mukaunti ya trans-nzoia balindilile kamakobosia mubukeli bwe kamafuki ka DNA ke  babandu balomekha khukhwira omukeni omunalirambo wa Switzerland nio mbo bolane khuyilwa musiina kumwesi kuno nekuli 27 khufunanisibwa kumusango kwe bubwiri.

column1: Omuruki Kenyatta asubisia khulonda kali muripoti ye ekokwa yakhalabanila butinyu bwe bulimi bwe kimiba kie esukari
column2: Omuruki  we lirambo  Uhuru Kenyatta ,asubisie balimi be kimiba mwirambo mbo serekali echa khulonda kosi kali muripoti yang’onilwe ne ekokwa yaroborwa khukhosia mubutinyu bulanyasianga bulimi bwe kimiba kie esukari mwirambo alala ne khuenjelesia chingila che khumala butinyu obwo.

column1: Serekali ekhongo erebwa khukhwingilila akari khuesia chisike chichingile mwirambo
column2: Omurangilisi we lukongo lwa Ndivis mwisasa lie bujumbe lie ewebuye ye ebukwe Martin Wanyonyi Pepela nono enya omuruki we lirambo uhuru kenyatta are abuwanga  khukhwingila khwe chisike mwirambo lino khuba  sinyasio sie lirambo.

column1: Omusikari wa AP okholanga kimilimo muofisi ya DP Ruto anyolekhna nafwilile munju yewe
column2:
Omupolisi we buuli ap olinda bikuka bio omulondela wo omuruki william ruto khunju ya harambee annex nairobi amakhunyolekha nafwile munju mwewe imara daima nairobi.
chabari chibola chili omupolisi oyo oli ne libale lia sergent khwisina kenei aba khumilimo endalo niyo waba waba omusibayi musikuka sie kiminyawe rashid echesa nende babandu babili khukhwama enje we lirambo bengila mubikuka ebio.echesa nende babandu abo babele nebafunanisibwa kumusango kwe khukhwituba mundakano ye ekontrasi ye bukuli bwe bulwane bwe banamae bwe chirupia chibilioni 39 bukhali bwang’ali ta.
ne nono bapolisi babola bali kenei anyolekhe ne chimbala che chindolio khumurwe mwiba libonekhana nga khukhwiyira.

column1: Chisike eli dalili ye sisyaumba basakhulu be Bungoma bara abuwanga
column2: Basakhulu mukokwa ye basakhulu babukusu mukaunti ye ebungoma nebarangililwa nende Bonface wanyonyi alala nende benard barasa bechile abuwanga ne khulangilila banakenya khukhwikanila ebweni wa wele nio mbo wele olane khumala chisike chichilile khusalikha mwirambo ne khukhwonakaka bimelwa mukaunti chindala.khulondekhana nende basakhulu abo chisike chili sili silamo khukhwama khuwele khubandu bakhamuria tawe. luno luri chikaunti 17 mwirambo chabele nechiatulwa ne chisike ne khukholela buri mubamenya khulondela bubwonakaki bwe bimelwa biabwe ne chisike echo.

column1: Bakhala babaebwa chikontrasi nende Spika we ekaunti ya Trans
column2: Balala khubakhala babaebwa chikontrasi che bukhala nende nakibondo we ebunge ye Trans-Nzoia Joshua Werunga ,barikhirisie khucha musiina khumufunana kumusango enyuma we khuloba khubarunga chirupia khubukhala bwabwe.

column1: Ba MCA be ebungoma baukhana munganakani nende Omwami Waluke khulondela khurusibwa khwe babasiabwe baroborwa
column2: Balala khubarangilisi be muchingongo mubunge ye ekaunti ye ebungoma balikhabekicha kumulomwa kwo omujumbe wa sirisia omwami John Waluke mbo barangilisi be muchingongo babaroborwa nende bamenya mubunge eyo bekhikhile khunula babasiabwe babaroborwa ne kimikanda kie bukhangarani mubunge eyo bubweyangu mukokwa chichaukhane mubunge eyo.

column1: Omwana afwa enyuma we khukwa mwiloo lie kamechi Malanga Malava kakamega
column2: Sibela ne kamasika bili mubamenya musirekere sia  Malanga mwisasa lie bujumbe lia  Malava  mukaunti ya   Kakamega  enyuma wo omwana we kimiko kitaru khufwa enyuma we  khukwa mwiloo lie kamechi lie buleyi bwe chifuti 25.

column1: Gavana Khaemba elochela sikelo sititi sie chirupia siebwa serekali che chikaunti khukhwimelela kamakhuwa ke bulamu
Gavanor Khaemba kenya bakholi ba serikali khuandikwa kimilimo khuchicontrasi
column2: Gavana wa Trans-nzoia Patrick simiyu khaemba nono abola mbo bwakhabele bulayi serikali che mucounty khuebwa bulekhule bwa khurobora bakholi khucontrasi.khulondekhana ne khaemba, abo babaroborwa kimilimo kia khumenya babechanga bakara .abulilile ali kachakisie bumenelesi khubakholi bano alala ne bubwifwi bwa bifaa bia ecounty.

column1: LSK Court coronavirus
column2: Kumukanda kwa banamalaka mwirambo lino LSK  kwachile musina khuyingilila serikali khwimekha chindeke khukhuama China khwicha mwirambo nabwila bulwale bwa coronavirus nabulikhalabanilwa.

column1: NARCK
column2:
Kiongozi wa esiama sia NARC- Kenya  Martha Karua katubane ne banakenya ne viongozi babandi khweuma serikali khumukhosi kwa khwiyamana ba chines 239 khwingila mwirambo lino.
nalomaloma amumukhung’ano ne banamakhua, abulilile ali serikali ya kenya seli bureke khumanana ne bulwale bwa coronavirus obwo niba bwingila mwirambo lino tawe

column1: Omuchinese khubandwa Athi River
Balimi chielefu 10 khukhwama mufamily chikhenyalila tawe banyola embolela ya busa
column2:
Balimi angaki wa chifuma likhumi na saba bakhenyalila tawe nakhulimo namulekhwa ne bakofu khukhuama mucounty ya ebungoma bacha khunyola embolela nende embeko khukhuama khuserikali ye ecounty ya ebungoma.kano kali khulondekhana ne gavana wycliffe wafula wangamati olomalome mumulukha kwa khuchakisia rasmi bukhalabani bwa khuana birumikhwa bino kukuchilile musisomelo sia bufundi sia naitiri mulukongo lwa mbakalo mulisasa lia bujumbe lia Tongaren.
wangamati arumikhile kumulukha okwo khunyanya lirafu khu afisa yesi yesi ocha khunyolekha naana birumikhwa ebio khubandu bakharoborwa tawe.

column1: Busolo sugar task force
column2: Owendebe wa kumukanda kwa balimi be kimiba kwa cha Kenya National Alliance of Sugar cane Farmers Organisation Saul Busolo nono kenya balimi baebwe bulekhule bwa khukusia kimiba kiabwe mukampuni niyo benya, ebodi ya esukari ekhakobola tawe ne lundi kamarumbi ka serikali kakusibwe khubandu binafsi.

column1: Busilikhi Lugulu
column2: Likangilo lie emisieni lia Lugulu liama khuba nelinyola buirumikhwa biaukhane bie busilikhi khubirira khumukanda kwa WECOHAS  khukhalabanila balwale balwala bikumba alala nende abo benyekha siaro  khwama mwirambo lie ebumerica  bibiolana angaki we chirupia chimilioni 50.

column1: Serikali ya kitaifa ebukula bubwimelesi bwe kaunty ya Nairobi
column2: Serikali ya kitaifa yabukule bubwimelesi bwe kaunty ya Nairobi.kano kecha busa enyuma wa gavana mike soko khulekhula bubwimelesi obwo mumakhono ka serikali ya kitaifa khukhwamanana nende chikesi che bukhalukha nicho bamuyila mukoti.Sonko kalekhulilwe bubwami obwo ebweni womuruki uhuru kenyataaa alala nende waziri we sikuka sie chingongo eugen wamalwa alala nende spika we senet keneth lusaka.chindalakho chiwizara nekhulimo eyo ya mipango, ye limotole, yebubwombakhi alala nende eyo ye chibarabara bise bino chili mumikhono kia serikali ya kitaifa.

column1: Omupeni wafuma mubabukusu Samuel Namatete khwisina lilindi Namatete kimuka Afwile
column2: Lifwa lio omupeni we kimienya ne bukhino bwe babukusu    wafuma Samuel Namatete mabwibwi kaluno liachilile khusindusia chinganakani che basime be kimienya kiewe.
